txt.en: 'Other Men come after many years and cut down forest. Some Drúedain die.'
'Other Drúedain leave this land. My ancestors stay here.'
'Long ago, Drúedain live on island with Men. We left island for land one day.'
'We came to these shores. Other left for shores far west of here.'
'One day Drúedain cross wide river and settle in shadow of this great mountain.'
'We first to settle on all sides of mountain. Drúedain were first here.'
